1
00:00:37,759 --> 00:00:38,920
Watch your mouth

2
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,880
So what if I have a dirty mouth?

3
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,479
Not only do I have a dirty mouth,

4
00:00:42,679 --> 00:00:43,560
my hands are itching, too

5
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:44,359
Stop!

6
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,280
Old man, get out of the way

7
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,600
Don't get yourself killed!

8
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:54,880
Teach this rude punk a lesson

9
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:58,399
Even collecting debts has rules

10
00:00:58,920 --> 00:00:59,320
Yes

11
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,079
I was wrong, I was wrong!

12
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:04,040
100,000 yuan

13
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:05,239
The Zhang family's debt

14
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,400
I've paid it off for them

15
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:10,359
If you ever bully them again,

16
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:12,799
it won't end with a few slaps

17
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:13,920
Yes, yes

18
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:14,879
I know I was wrong

19
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:15,840
I know I was wrong

20
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,560
The IOU

21
00:01:20,359 --> 00:01:21,280
The IOU

22
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,560
Thank you, Master Long

23
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:31,799
For what?

24
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,480
From now on, I'm your Master

25
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:35,840
Handling things for you,

26
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:37,560
Isn't that my job?

27
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:53,760
Master Long, please accept my respect.

28
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,400
Your disciple wishes to take you as Master

29
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:57,640
From now on,

30
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:00,000
you're basically my son

31
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:03,120
The Long family is your home, too

32
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,800
I left the US for Benevolence Hospital

33
00:02:09,159 --> 00:02:10,080
because you promised

34
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,319
you'd build a Cancer Center

35
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,719
and fully support my research

36
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:13,800
I know

37
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:15,560
The Cancer Center will definitely be built.

38
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:18,560
It's just that funding has hit some problems

39
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,599
Could you give me a little more time?

40
00:02:21,719 --> 00:02:22,360
To be honest,

41
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,120
a hospital in Korea is contacting me right now

42
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:27,520
Their terms beat Benevolence Hospital's.

43
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,759
I'm not someone who breaks my word

44
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:31,000
but I have to make sure

45
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,759
my research project gets completed

46
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,240
I understand what you need

47
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:37,120
Just give me a little more time

48
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,319
I'll give you a satisfactory answer.

49
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,639
I can only give you three days

50
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,039
If within three days

51
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,879
your project's funding isn't sorted out,

52
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,039
I'll accept the Korean hospital's offer.

53
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,360
Thank you

54
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,280
I heard

55
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,560
the Cancer Center has run into trouble

56
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:08,520
Several banks won't give us a loan

57
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:11,639
I do have a proposal

58
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,199
that could help you solve this

59
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:14,400
Let's hear it

60
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,879
Prosperity Group and Benevolence Hospital

61
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:19,759
will jointly establish a Care Fund

62
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,000
Fifty percent equity each

63
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,560
This fund will mainly be used for

64
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,520
building the Cancer Center

65
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,479
And the rest

66
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:27,840
will go toward giving those

67
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,719
poor families who can't afford surgery

68
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,000
the help they need.

69
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:33,400
How much will Prosperity Group invest?

70
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:34,280
50 million

71
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,159
Right now, I

72
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,280
can't come up with 50 million

73
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,199
I actually considered that

74
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,560
You don't have to put in cash

75
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:45,800
But

76
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,520
you must use Benevolence Hospital shares

77
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,159
as collateral

78
00:03:49,639 --> 00:03:50,520
Because this fund

79
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,599
is mainly for building the Cancer Center,

80
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,960
Benevolence Hospital must take the lead

81
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,960
and you will be the fund's administrator

82
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,199
So if you don't invest,

83
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,560
to Prosperity Group,

84
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,159
it'll be hard for me to explain.

85
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,159
I understand

86
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,759
But Benevolence Hospital's shares

87
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,080
are very important to me

88
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:11,639
Before my dad died,

89
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:13,280
this was the last thing he left me

90
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,600
Actually,

91
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,160
even if you pledge Benevolence Hospital

92
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:21,959
shares to the fund,

93
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,720
they will actually still be yours.

94
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,120
Because control of the fund

95
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,279
will still be in your hands

96
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,680
Right now, your goal

97
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:31,279
is to ensure the Cancer Center is built.

98
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:40,120
Fine, then I'll invest with my shares

99
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,120
Then let's get this done quickly

100
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,800
Dr. Yiwen Zhang only gave me three days

101
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,519
No problem

102
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:47,399
Prosperity Group's funds will arrive soon.

103
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,000
I now announce

104
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:59,279
the Care Fund is officially established

105
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,040
Good

106
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,800
Brother Xiaobei

107
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,439
Brother Xiaobei!

108
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,240
What are you doing here?

109
00:05:28,519 --> 00:05:29,560
I missed you so much

110
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:31,240
so I took an overnight flight to see you.

111
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,279
Let's go

112
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:34,639
Let's go have some fun

113
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,240
I've still got work to do

114
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,759
What work?

115
00:05:39,319 --> 00:05:40,439
Look at all these antiques

116
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:41,959
I haven't finished appraising them

117
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,480
I'll buy all of them

118
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:52,120
Then we can go out and have fun

119
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,120
Come on

120
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:03,120
What can you put inside this?

121
00:06:03,519 --> 00:06:06,120
You can add all kinds of vegetables.

122
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:07,240
Then I want all of them

123
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,160
Okay, okay, okay

124
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,240
Hold on a second

125
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,800
Lisa

126
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:13,199
Si Qi

127
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,680
What brings you here?

128
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:17,519
We heard Uncle is better and discharged.

129
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,399
so we came by to see you

130
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,439
Yuanzhou, Si Qi, you're here

131
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,199
Yuanzhou

132
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,920
Thanks again for last time

133
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,680
Otherwise, your uncle surely would've...

134
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,800
I heard Uncle was back,

135
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,639
so I came with Si Qi to see you all

136
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,120
We've already eaten

137
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,120
Here, Uncle

138
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:31,600
You're too kind

139
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,240
Yours is ready.

140
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,240
Thank you, Auntie

141
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,600
Come on, Yuanzhou, Si Qi

142
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,360
You two have a taste, too

143
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,480
Have a bite

144
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:37,000
Here

145
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,160
I'll pass

146
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,680
Don't you like eating this too?

147
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,959
This smells so good.

148
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:49,720
Brother Xiaobei!

149
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,040
Your pancakes are really delicious.

150
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,600
I'm glad you like it.

151
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,720
Will I gain weight if I eat this?

152
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:56,000
Don't worry.

153
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,399
Add as much as you want.

154
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,480
You won't get fat.

155
00:06:58,759 --> 00:06:59,759
Then I want to add some of this too.

156
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:00,600
Add a little more.

157
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:04,360
I love this too.

158
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:08,480
And that one too.

159
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,439
She's not right for you.

160
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,079
She doesn't even see you.

161
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:14,800
I know.

162
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:17,680
You may not be able to let go right away.

163
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:19,199
Enough, enough, enough.

164
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:21,079
But I'll keep waiting for you.

165
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:24,240
This really smells amazing.

166
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,480
They're really just my good friends.

167
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,839
It's so tasty.

168
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:32,959
You try a bite too.

169
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:44,160
I asked you here today about work.

170
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:44,839
I wanted to talk to you.

171
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,160
Go ahead.

172
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,120
The Cancer Center went over budget.

173
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:51,839
The fund doesn't have enough to cover it.

174
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,680
Can Prosperity Group invest a bit more?

175
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,519
I'm afraid that'll be tough.

176
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:01,879
Because this project

177
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:04,199
was only approved because I pushed for it.

178
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,759
You know Prosperity Group's style.

179
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:09,079
They don't want to invest in

180
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,839
charities with little return.

181
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,079
So what do we do now?

182
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,040
Don't worry.

183
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,720
I thought it over.

184
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:17,839
How about this:

185
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,439
First, transfer your pledged shares

186
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:20,839
to Prosperity Group,

187
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:22,680
which means selling them to me.

188
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,959
I'll cash out to cover the emergency.

189
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:28,399
You can buy them back when things improve.

190
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:34,840
Okay.

191
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,360
We'll do it your way.

192
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,559
Good. Very good.

193
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,559
I didn't expect you'd so easily

194
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:48,399
take over Benevolence Medical.

195
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,960
That's my son.

196
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:51,080
Father.

197
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,000
Since I've passed your test,

198
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,039
shouldn't you honor

199
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:57,279
the promise you made me?

200
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:59,679
That last investment in Benevolence Medical

201
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,799
you handled it well.

202
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:01,759
But it's not enough.

203
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,720
If you accomplish one more thing,

204
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:07,240
then you'll truly pass.

205
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,120
What is it?

206
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,960
Acquire Benevolence Medical.

207
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,600
As long as you succeed,

208
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:14,679
you'll be Prosperity Group's heir.

209
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:16,840
No problem.

210
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,879
I'll call a shareholder meeting tomorrow.

211
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,360
I now announce

212
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:23,080
my son, Sheng Yuanzhou, as of today,

213
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,120
is officially Prosperity Group's heir.

214
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,960
He'll fully participate in group business

215
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,039
to prepare to take over.

216
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,159
Please welcome him.

217
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,240
Once you've chosen,

218
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:37,879
there's no turning back.

219
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,840
Only by becoming a king

220
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:44,320
can you be the final winner.

221
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,039
Si Qi.

222
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:01,559
Sheng Yuanzhou.

223
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,639
This was all your trap, wasn't it?

224
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,799
You made Dr. Yiwen Zhang leave.

225
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:07,000
You told the bank

226
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,480
not to lend to my family, right?

227
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:09,440
Why?

228
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,440
Say something. Why?

229
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,039
Since you're so desperate to know,

230
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:14,159
I'll tell you the truth.

231
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:15,799
Because I want Benevolence Medical.

232
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:16,639
But...

233
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,159
You knew perfectly well

234
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:21,480
that was my dad's life's work.

235
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,279
Mercy has no place in war;

236
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,320
scruples have no place in business.

237
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:25,759
Having a soft heart is no way to make money.

238
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:28,000
That slap just now

239
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,759
counts as repaying your trust in me.

240
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:31,679
Sheng Yuanzhou, you...

241
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,200
You bastard!

242
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:34,679
Sheng Yuanzhou!

243
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,279
Let go of me!

244
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:48,279
Everyone.

245
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,639
Just a minor interruption. Don't mind it.

246
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,679
From here on,

247
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:54,720
I'll be counting on your guidance.

248
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,600
She trusted you so much.

249
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,600
Why did you hurt her?

250
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,279
And you didn't hurt her?

251
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:13,120
You kept saying you liked her,

252
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:14,840
so why didn't you stay by her side?

253
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:17,080
Instead you let a bastard like me step in.

254
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,200
Isn't that because of you?

255
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,240
Don't pin the blame on me.

256
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:22,039
You're the one who's weak and useless.
